1
00:00:00,270 --> 00:00:04,630
[Previously]
Do you think he knows that his boyfriend in the game is actually me?

2
00:00:04,630 --> 00:00:07,100
Actually, I knew it all along.

3
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:08,830
But that's in the game.

4
00:00:08,830 --> 00:00:12,090
If you are scared like this all the time, how can you and Near be together?

5
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:13,729
What the hell are you doing?

6
00:00:13,730 --> 00:00:16,030
Somebody may like it this way,

7
00:00:16,030 --> 00:00:18,550
but not me.

8
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:28,770
Where is Tong Fah at?

9
00:00:42,290 --> 00:00:47,770
Fah, are you hurt a lot?

10
00:00:49,010 --> 00:00:51,910
Please get up...

11
00:00:51,910 --> 00:00:55,030
You're the one who asked me out.

12
00:01:21,610 --> 00:01:27,310
He's probably tired, so let's let him sleep first.

13
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:40,000
I got something for you.

14
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:52,480
Fah was holding onto this when the emergency rescue came.

15
00:01:53,980 --> 00:01:56,640
I think he wanted to give it to you.

16
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:12,660
It's all my fault.

17
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:17,080
It's my fault...

18
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,980
Thank you for being a part of my life.

19
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:55,500
Ever since my dad passed away, other than Mom,

20
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:58,900
you're the reason that I was able to remain bright.

21
00:02:58,900 --> 00:03:06,959
You're the one who brought brightness into my dark sky.

22
00:03:06,959 --> 00:03:09,779
I'm always telling myself that

23
00:03:09,779 --> 00:03:15,320
the way I feel about you is because

24
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:20,659
we've known each other for a long time and we're good friends.

25
00:03:20,659 --> 00:03:25,360
But now... I know that it's not like that.

26
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:30,280
Paper, I love you.

27
